arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	--Stop whispers if player skips
	Hydra.ActorPlaySound (idTreeAudioLoc, sTreeOfWhispersStop)
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idTreeAudioLoc)
	
	idLorathFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	idNeyrelleFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Neyrelle_Follower_Magic")
	
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idNeyrelleFollower)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorathFollower, idSnakeTravelTrigger, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorathFollower, idSnakeTravelTrigger, true)
	--Hydra.QActorSheath(idLorathFollower)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelleFollower, NeyrelleSnakeLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idNeyrelleFollower)
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	Hydra.EventSend("LorathMoved")
end

function Start()

	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convNeyrelleSnake, idNeyrelle)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convNeyrelleSnake)
	
	SetTraversalEnabled(idTraversalKiller4, true)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelle, SnakeWalkLoc01, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelle, SnakeWalkLoc02, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)

	Hydra.QActorWait(idLorath, 1)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorath, SnakeWalkLoc01, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorath, SnakeWalkLoc02, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)

	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idNeyrelle)
	Hydra.QActorPower(idNeyrelle, powerTraversal, idSnakeJumpTraversal, true)

	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idLorath)
	Hydra.QActorPower(idLorath, powerTraversal, idSnakeJumpTraversal, true)

	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelle, NeyrelleTreeLoc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorath, LorathTreeLoc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idNeyrelle, NeyrelleTreeLoc)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorath, LorathTreeLoc)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idLorath)
	Hydra.EventSend("FinallyAtTree")

end
